race.comment: Competitive. A DIME APPROACH (2) peaks and will appreciate the step up to the middle distance. Has the blinkers on again and finally draws an inside gate. AMERICAN GAS (7) races forward and has been racing at Warrnambool in better grade since the Maiden win there. Well placed and is sure to give a sight. ASEVENTY SEVEN (3) finds easier and will be suited stepping up from a mile. On a 7-day return and rates a player. TRIOMPHE (5) can do better than recent efforts.
